## Principally of the genus ''[[Asclepias]]'' in order [[Gentianales]], family [[Apocynaceae]]
## Also of the genus ''[[Calotropis]]'' in order [[Gentianales]], family [[Apocynaceae]]
## {{taxlink|Euphorbia peplus|species|noshow=1|ver=161014}} and {{taxlink|Euphorbia heterophylla|species|noshow=1|ver=161014}}, in order [[Malpighiales]].
# A [[monarch butterfly]].

